The paper discusses the use of deep neural networks and transfer learning for performance modeling, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The study also involves empirical analysis and experimentation, which could be classified under software engineering (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper discusses the impact of different hardware environments on performance, which could be categorized under computer architecture (cs.AR) and systems and control (cs.SY).
